snippet.title: Wheel Runner - Playtester Edition - Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the Playtesting for Wheel Runner by going to franchovy.itch.io/wheel-runner

Wheel Runner is a game where you crank to spin a wheel forward, and you have to do it fast! Collect all the coins and complete each level under a certain time to receive all the stars!
